summary: A playable save game female Night-Elf character. Pretty sure she looks quite like a Night-Elf. People who plays world of Warcraft hopefully will like it, couple of mods are required for this save file to work properly.... And thankz
descriptionHtml:
[b][center][font=Comic Sans MS]
[quote][color=#00ffff]First Of All None Of The Mods Are MINE NONE!! I just used a couple of mods for making a character which looks like a night elf.I just take credits for customizing a female Epic Elf(race mod) into a night Elf.[/color][/quote]Not a perfect Night-Elf but this is what I could do In SKYRIM... If you can do better please be sure to share your one too :D
[/font][/center][/b][list=1][*]_You can alter the Heights using console {showracemenu} as because Night-Elves are teller, but I just kept it that way so you guyz can alter them yourself.[/*]
